  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cyclone Idai Phase 2A</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The needs of the communities affected by the cyclone Idai continue to be there, and have been worsened by COVID-19. Christian Aid continues to support those communities, and has adapted its response to the pandemic.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Outcomes:
- Target communities have improved access to potable water and good health and hygiene information and services 
- Target communities have improved capacity to prepare for, anticipate and deal with the effects of disaster and climate change
- Target communities have improved access to community based psychosocial support and GBV awareness information and services</narrative>
  </description>
